com.cmput301f17t07.ingroove.DataManagers.Command

Interface DataManagerAPI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataManager, MockDataManager

    public interface DataManagerAPI
    [Facade Interface] An interface which represents all the methods for frontend objects to interact with the data. All frontend objects, which need data, should contain a reference to a DataManagerAPI object so that they can call the methods listed below. Both the real and mock data manager facades should implement this interface. Created by fraserbulbuc on 2017-11-07.
